headline: Umicore - Transparency notifications by BlackRock, Inc.
summary: Transparency notifications byBlackRock, Inc. In accordance with article 14, § 1 of the law of 2 May 2007 on the disclosure of major holdings, Umicore was recently notified by BlackRock, Inc. that it has successively crossed the legal threshold of 3% for the direct voting rights upwards on 19 September 2025 and then downwards on 22 September 2025.
